00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,840
[EP. 01] Before I Reach You

2
00:00:18,940 --> 00:00:19,960
Man…

3
00:00:19,960 --> 00:00:21,660
Why is it raining all of the sudden?

4
00:00:21,660 --> 00:00:22,660
Huh?

5
00:00:22,660 --> 00:00:24,360
That’s the guy from the elective class!

6
00:00:25,180 --> 00:00:26,540
Hel..hello?

7
00:00:32,840 --> 00:00:33,860
Hello.

8
00:00:35,740 --> 00:00:37,220
Are you taking the bus here?

9
00:00:37,240 --> 00:00:37,740
Yes.

10
00:00:38,140 --> 00:00:40,160
Are you going home?

11
00:00:40,660 --> 00:00:41,160
Yes.

12
00:00:41,860 --> 00:00:44,380
Is he a “Yes Man” or what?

13
00:00:44,380 --> 00:00:46,380
Leaving me just hanging there…

14
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:49,400
Ah?!

15
00:00:50,560 --> 00:00:52,740
It’s going to tear apart…

16
00:00:57,260 --> 00:00:59,260
Argh…It’s bothering me…

17
00:01:01,300 --> 00:01:01,800
Argh!

18
00:01:16,940 --> 00:01:18,520
This is nuts.

19
00:01:18,960 --> 00:01:20,640
So embarrassing.

20
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:23,160
He must think I’m a weirdo.

21
00:01:23,540 --> 00:01:25,760
Ha… Should I apologize?

22
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,380
He’d probably just say “yes”.

23
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:34,320
But…I should apologize, huh?

24
00:01:36,560 --> 00:01:38,740
Umm… hey…

25
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:53,520
What the…What’s up with him?

26
00:01:54,320 --> 00:01:57,340
Relationship; built on simple actions

27
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:03,000
Ah… I should have given the umbrella…

28
00:02:04,380 --> 00:02:10,960
A Day Before Us

